These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite
There are 2 different nationalities: egyptian, polish
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, engineer
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: documentary, sports
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: azalea, sunflower
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, july
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, taxi
1. the polish is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the accountant##1
4. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Beverage      | sprite     | hot-chocolate |
| Nationality         | polish  | egyptian       |
| Job           | engineer   | accountant    |
| Movie-Genre   | sports     | documentary   |
| Flower   | sunflower      | azalea     |
| Birthday         | july | august      |
| Transport     | taxi       | bus           |

