.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-2::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, september
There 2 different types of food: avocado, strawberry
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: baseball, swimming
City: hannover, miami
There are 2 different nationalities: thai, turkish
2 different pets are kept: cat, rat
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, van
1. the person traveling to hannover is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
3. the person traveling to miami is in an odd position##4
4. the turkish is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
5. the person who's birthday is in july is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |
| Birthday      | september         | july       |
| Food          | avocado        | strawberry |
| Sport           | swimming | baseball    |
| City   | miami        | hannover  |
| Nationality   | turkish        | thai       |
| Pet           | rat            | cat        |
| Transport     | van            | ship       |

