2 different games are played: go, bridge
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, volleyball
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, february
1. the person playing go is on the right of the russian##1
2. the person drinking fanta is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in june is the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the british is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
6. the fisherman is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Job           | journalist    | fisherman  |
